    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Despite the Not accepted decision framing in the COU description, the credibility assessment team formally records this package as accepted for archival and regulatory submission purposes pending remediation plan. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed and is discussed throughout the assessment narrative; however, not all validation results carry formally linked UQ artifacts — in particular, the peak wall shear stress comparison and hemolysis submodel scalar transport result reference uncertainty considerations only in prose. Remediation of the six not-assessed factors and formal linking of UQ artifacts to all validation results is required before re-submission at MRL 5.",
